<div style="background:linear-gradient(135deg, #dbeafe, #bfdbfe); padding:1.25rem; border-radius:12px; margin:1.5rem 0;">
  <p style="font-weight:700; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">💡 Rain Intensity Scale</p>
  <p style="margin:0;">Chinese has specific words for rain intensity: <strong>小雨</strong> (xiǎo yǔ, light rain) → <strong>中雨</strong> (zhōng yǔ, moderate rain) → <strong>大雨</strong> (dà yǔ, heavy rain) → <strong>暴雨</strong> (bào yǔ, torrential rain). The same pattern works for snow: 小雪, 中雪, 大雪, 暴雪.</p>
</div>

