<p><strong>Temperature sentences:</strong></p>
<ul>
  <li>今天几度？(Jīntiān jǐ dù?) — What's the temperature today?</li>
  <li>今天三十五度。(Jīntiān sānshíwǔ dù.) — It's 35 degrees today.</li>
  <li>零下十度。(Língxià shí dù.) — Minus 10 degrees.</li>
  <li>今天比昨天热。(Jīntiān bǐ zuótiān rè.) — Today is hotter than yesterday.</li>
</ul>

